description:
A new generation of fashion retail and resell platform.
F1ZZ is a liquidity network for scarce viral commodities (SVC) by creating perpetual contract that allows frictionless trading of semi-fungible tokens.
In the F1ZZ network, speculators long/short a fraction of a SVC, buyers and sellers trade a variety of SVC effortlessly, members can participate in the ISO (initial shoe offering), and influencers may engage in the live streaming selling. F1ZZ establish a value network for speculators, collectors, manufacturers, influencers, authenticators and distributors in the retail, resell, and ISO primary market.
name: F1ZZ
